                    <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                        In emergencies, <strong class="text-gray-100">every second matters</strong>. Often, victims are unable to speak, unlock their phones, or explain who to contact. Ekam Care was created to solve this critical gap.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                        The Ekam Care Emergency Card ensures that any nearby person can help by simply scanning a QR code. Within seconds, family members receive an emergency alert along with the cardholder's <strong class="text-gray-100">real-time location</strong>, enabling faster response and immediate action.
                    </p>
                    <div class="bg-red-900/20 border-l-4 border-red-600 p-6 rounded-r-xl">
